    "This is a mission game, not a treasure hunt - no treasures to collect",
    "Color-coded security system: white (visitor) < yellow (maintenance) < blue (security)",
    "ID badges are created in the grey chair room using colored keys and buttons",
    "Each colored door requires at least that clearance level: white=visitor+, yellow=maintenance+, blue=security only",
    "The tape recorder from the briefing room jams the control room door open",
    "Wire cutters are needed to cut alarm wires (window) and bomb wire (reactor)",
    "The pail must be filled with water from the heavy water vat in storage",
    "POUR WATER in the break room defuses the bomb (win). POUR WATER in the control room triggers it (lose)",
    "The anti-radiation suit protects you in the reactor core area",
    "TV cameras at security doors check your badge - SHOW PICTURE to pass",
    "The yellow key is found on the ledge outside the visitors room window",
    "The film cartridge in the control room can be loaded into the projector for information"
  ],
